cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.SY

This paper is about a framework for automated quantization of deep neural networks, which involves reinforcement learning and hardware simulation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, since the paper deals with hardware accelerators and resource constraints, it could also belong to cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
